        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-0 mb-2">üì± iOS Screen Time</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 m-0 text-sm">Protect iPhones and iPads in your household</p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/guides/android-family-link"
        class="block bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 no-underline transition-all hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
