        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-0 mb-2">ü§ñ Android Family Link</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 m-0 text-sm">Manage Android devices with similar controls</p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/guides/gaming-consoles"
        class="block bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 no-underline transition-all hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-0 mb-2">üéÆ Gaming Consoles</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 m-0 text-sm">Extend protection to Xbox and other gaming systems</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
      <strong>Complete Protection:</strong> Combine Family Safety (Windows controls) + DNS filtering (all browsers) + regular
      communication (education) for the most effective approach.
    </div>
